    public class ComicPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Class to create a comic panel. A comic panel will have a picture and can have one or more text balloons. It uses a JLabel to show the picture.
    Author:
    Barb Ericson ericson@cc.gatech.edu Copyright 2005
